wiki.text:
'Shu' may refer to:
* Shu (Egyptian deity)
* 蜀 (Shǔ), an abbreviation of Sichuan province of the People's Republic of
  China, as well as the following historical regimes that have existed in this
  region: **Shu (state) (蜀国/蜀國 or 古蜀), a state during the Zhou Dynasty era (c.
  1046 BCE – c. 316) **Shu Han (蜀汉/蜀漢), a state that existed during the Three
  Kingdoms Period (221–263) **Cheng Han (成汉/成漢), also named Later Shu (后蜀/後蜀),
  one of the Sixteen Kingdoms (304–347) **Western Shu (西蜀), also named Qiao Shu
  (谯蜀/譙蜀), one of the units of the Eastern Jin period (405–413) **Former Shu
  (前蜀), one of the divisions of the Five Dynasties and Ten Kingdoms period
  (907–925) **Later Shu (后蜀/後蜀), one of the divisions of the Five Dynasties and
  Ten Kingdoms period (934–965)
* the Kazakh name for the Chui River
* Shu, Kazakhstan
* The ancient Chinese [[Classic of History]] (Shū 書)

;People
* Shu, the guitarist in the Japanese rock band, BACK-ON
* Frank Shu (born 1943), Chinese-American professor of astronomy
* Dong Zhongshu, Han Dynasty Chinese scholar
* Shu Shibutani (born 1979), Japanese professional wrestler

;Fictional characters
* Shu, the main character in the Xbox 360 game Blue Dragon
* Shu, a character in the [[Dragon Ball]] franchise
* Shu (''Suikoden''), a character in the video game Suikoden II
* Shu Shirakawa, a recurring character in the [[Super Robot Wars]] video
  game series
* Shū, a fictional character in the Fist of the North Star manga and
  anime franchise
* Shu, a fictional character in the manga series [[Hikaru no Go]]
* Shuzo "Shu" Matsutani, a character in the anime series [[Now and Then, Here
  and There]] and [[Legendz]]

'SHU' may be an acronym for: *Sacred Heart University, in Fairfield, Connecticut
*Scoville Heat Unit, a measurement of hotness or spiciness in food *Security
Housing Unit, a solitary confinement space in a maximum security prison *Seton
Hall University, in South Orange, New Jersey *Seton Hill University, in
Greensburg, Pennsylvania *Shanghai University (上海大学), in Shanghai, China
*Sheffield Hallam University, a modern university in Northern England *Shih Hsin
University (世新大學), in Taipei, Taiwan *Special Handling Unit, a super maximum
security prison located in Sainte-Anne-des-Plaines, Quebec
